{"tid":1018612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"細數中共攻陷香港方法","createTime":"2019-02-12T11:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T12:46:35.000Z","uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de2893e8e64ccef45afc81f3e3c452045cf529ff","tid":1018612,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:11:12.000Z","msg":"1.人口大洗牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日150人落 重要每個生兩三個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上，小中學隨便一班應該都有5個係蝗<br />\n<br />\n2.香港人普遍低民族意識<br />\n當你發現香港唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有錢就走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有能力想叫你去大灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇錢留係度，但你冇咩影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3.語言 文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸一出咩逗音同咩直播 <br />\n旺角 深水埗等地區會有人推廣<br />\n你下載就送你野之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普教中，細路成口蝗語 咩牛逼之類<br />\n<br />\n4.交通<br />\n打通交通 方便車你上去之外<br />\n更方便係叫蝗落港 <br />\n吸納蝗醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5.政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直下人才奶爆共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n錢你又送哂俾中共 人係又中共<br />\n你走定留係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2c8ca222623db13b4bc95f7f56112114bf2a55","tid":1018612,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:34:55.000Z","msg":"1.唔只5個喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e20b4a309e76922e86a4bdabba52b660543948","tid":1018612,"uid":82482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:42:36.000Z","msg":"收編傳媒，紙媒，電台，電視台<br />\n<br />\n控制行政，立法兩會，以至整個政府<br />\n<br />\n聘用大量五毛於各論壇轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n文化入侵，普教，幼兒洗腦教育<br />\n<br />\n由中聯辦收編所有建制票源，動員，滴水不漏<br />\n<br />\n控制本地食材輸入，食水等<br />\n<br />\n推高物價/樓價，製造艱難生活，市民忙於糊口，無多餘精力講民主自由平等普世價值"},{"pid":"f140120690b1c345c70937ff99289fa0791c9c70","tid":1018612,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c2c8ca222623db13b4bc95f7f56112114bf2a55","tid":1018612,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:34:55.000Z","msg":"1.唔只5個喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:55:52.000Z","msg":"人口溝淡戰術大成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080beda883cc1f4c6ba8d19781c0fdd127bf5ace","tid":1018612,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}